<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.1">
<l>muntuṟa vuraikkēṉ viraikkuḻal maṭavār kalaviyai viṭutaṭu māṟal</l>
<l>antara mēḻu malaikaṭa lēḻu māyavem maṭikaḷtam kōyil</l>
<l>cantoṭu maṇiyu maṇimayil taḻaiyun taḻuvivan taruvikaḷ nirantu</l>
<l>vantiḻi cāral māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am speaking [up] since [this] is a priority:</l>
<l rend="indent">abandon embracing simple ladies with fragrant curls! [It’s] madness!</l>
<l>Come, simple heart; we will worship at Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">on whose slope cascades descend in spate,</l>
<l>Coming carrying sandalwood, jewels, and beautiful peacock feathers,</l>
<l>The temple of our god who became the seven interior [lands]</l>
<l rend="Indent">and the seven tossing seas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
